# Lead Details Page Refinement

Improve the lead details page by making the Spotify player functional, enlarging Instagram posts for better readability, and moving artist info to the banner.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> The Spotify player will now use a standard iframe embed. For the best experience, the artist's Spotify URL must be correctly populated. Chronological navigation through releases will remain functional via the "Previous/Next" buttons, which will update the iframe source.

